<TEXT>
president mikhail s gorbachev has acted to 
restore the rights of victims of josef stalin under whose rule 
millions of peasants died of starvation were shot or sent to labor 
camps as enemies of the people 
in his toughest condemnation yet of stalins forced 
collectivization of agriculture which began in the late 1920s 
