embargo it would probably cause domestic upheaval jordan has 
witnessed mass proiraqi demonstrations by palestinians and moslem 
fundamentalists 
but another analyst dore gold said the united states probably 
would not allow goods to reach iraq via aqaba because it would 
damage the effectiveness of international sanctions 
if there is any sense that the blockade or lets use the word 
quarantine is porous to a certain extent then immediately nations 
with greater mercantile interests will start trading with iraq 
said gold an analyst at the jaffee center for strategic studies at 
tel aviv university 
