from dinner theater to donahue a 
montanabased religious sect is working to mend an image tattered 
by a fuel spill at its underground fallout shelter near yellowstone 
national park 
it was four months ago that 31000 gallons of diesel and 
gasoline leaked from tanks buried near the church universal and 
