i know that it takes a minimum of two hours to pick up a deer 
and they usually have to drive 50 miles or more godshall said 
it can take two or three hours of an officers time its a 
tremendous bill 
the remedies for road kills are varied among them is more 
careful planning of where roads go reexamination of grasses and 
shrubs planted along roads dispensing with salt as a way of 
ridding roads of ice because deer like salt and more warning 
signs 
colorado and pennsylvania are considering rerouting deer over 
