1974 the study was conducted by the natioonal assessment of 
educational progress popularly known as the nations report card 
eighthgrade english teachers reported that 45 percent of their 
students wrote papers of a paragraph or two weekly and only 14 
percent wrote a oneor twopage paper each week only 6 percent 
wrote papers or three or more pages each year 
fortytwo percent of the teachers said they spend about one hour 
each week on instructing and helping students with writing 302 
percent spend 30 minutes or less 
the american association of parents amp children said four out of 
10 eleventh graders cannot write an adequate description of their 
qualifications for a job 
the pen pal discovery program provides freeofcharge 
letterwriting kits that explain the various types of letters and 
the different parts of each like the heading greeting body 
closing 
the kits also include special writing paper for letters to 
foster ideas about subject matter data pages are provided for 
children to record information about themselves their state and 
neighborhood 
teachers oversee use of the kits and are encouraged to 
incorporate the project into the regular classroom lessons once 
the letters are written individually in class the teacher sends 
them in a packet to the pen pals of the prematched class 
the pilot program also tried individual mailings of the letters 
officials conceded that method failed 
this school year students will send letters each month 
beginning in january 
judy lewis executive vice president at kelly said an 
information survey of the teachers found they liked the program 
because it is selfcontained wellorganized easy to follow and 
supports their curriculum 
classrooms are matched by computer with the purpose of pairing 
urban and rural schools schools in new york with those in 
california and schools with unique cultural differences said lewis 
there is nothing like this that we found exist said lewis 
there is nothing that takes the concept of pen pals communicating 
beyond giving them a pen pal and saying write 
we suggest what to write about give them materials to use to 
write back and forth and provide the setting under which it can 
occur 
lewis said kelly communications is asking corporations to 
provide financial support for the program the cost is estimated at 
3 per child 
