<TEXT>
united parcel service of america inc 
wasted no time letting customers know it was business as usual 
after the teamsters union announced its truck drivers and package 
handlers had ratified a new threeyear contract 
ups account executives started calling or visiting the companys 
11 million daily pickup customers monday to tell them the news 
