connecticut are slated to take the place of the services los 
angelesclass attack boats 
the nuclearpowered sub had been devised to counter what the 
pentagon saw as the rapidly improving capabilities of the soviet 
navy 
the burkeclass destroyer is designed to operate in carrier 
