which allow it to track and guide weapons to destroy multiple 
targets at any one time 
cheney said purchasing fewer of the vessels will allow the 
destroyers fighting capabilities to be upgraded through improving 
its electronics and antisubmarine weaponry 
the changes will mean one less destroyer in fiscal 1991 
